                            <filiation>Transcript of <title type="ms">Kringla</title> or <title type="ms">Codex Academicus Primus</title> which was destroyed at
                                the fire at Copenhagen University Library in <date when="1728">1728</date>. According to Jørgensen (<bibl>
                                        <ref type="secondary-1" target="BiblArn45">The Lost Vellum Kringla</ref>
                                </bibl>) AM 35–36–63 fol., together with Holm. Papp. 18 fol.,
                                constitute the most important transcripts of the lost
                                Kringla-manuscript.</filiation>
